{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1673-02_119", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Suite des Fragmens de la Comedie contre les Nouvellistes, où l’on voit tous les termes extraordinaires dont se servent ces Messieurs]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", tome II [mai-juillet 1672], 1673, p. 119-126."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "JE me rendis un de ces jours de cette Semaine d’assez bonne heure au Bureau, croyant que j’aurois le loisir de me promener quelque temps seul, & de réver à quelques Affaires que j’avois dans la teste ; mais je ne fus pas plutost entré que j’apperçeus le Nouvelliste Autheur qui travailloit à sa Piece. Il vint à moy dés qu’il m’eut apperçeu, & me dit qu’il me vouloit faire voir ce qu’il venoit de faire. C’est une Scene de ma Piece contre les Nouvellistes, adjouta-t-il ; & c’est de la mesme Femme dont je vous ay parlé. Voicy ce qu’elle dit aux Nouvellistes à qui elle demande son Mary."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Messieurs, je vous demande excuse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Et je croyois avecque vous"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Trouver mon faineant d’Epoux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui tous les jours icy s’amuse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Et fait le Nouvelliste au milieu de vingt fous."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "On luy répond,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’est-ce qu’un Nouvelliste ? il n’est je croy personne"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/l[2]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Que l’on appelle de ce nom,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et ce n’est qu’une vision."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Elle leur replique."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Vrayment vous nous la donnez bonne :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[2]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour moy je les connois fort bien,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et les ay veu causer ensemble,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[4]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Lors qu’une Nouvelle de rien"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[5]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Quelquefois icy les assemble."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Un Nouvelliste dit à part."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce qu’elle dit est une verité."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Elle poursuit."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "On en rencontre icy presque dans chaque Allée."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[2]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Ils s’appellent vostre Assemblée,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "La Compagnie & la Societé,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[4]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Ou le grand Bureau des Nouvelles,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui bien souvent ne sont que bagatelles."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Si quelqu’un d’entre eux vient trop tard,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[7]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Il dit d’une ame un peu dolente,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[8]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’il en aura pourtant sa part,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Quoy qu’il ne soit venu qu’à Nouvelle expirante,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[10]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’à l’heure des reflexions,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[11]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Et qu’au temps où les Politiques"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Font en parlant des Affaires publiques,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[13]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Redoubler les attentions."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Nouvelles, dit-il, ne sont bien asseurées,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[15]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’à ces heures là seulement ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[16]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Et l’on croit parfaitement,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Que quand par tels & tels elles sont averées,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[18]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui souvent ont l’honneur de voir"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[19]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[19]/text()[1]", "text": "Des Gens que leur employ contraint à tout sçavoir."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[20]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[20]/text()[1]", "text": "Si chacun, poursuit-il, a quitté l’Assemblée,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[21]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[21]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[21]/text()[1]", "text": "Quelque Nouvelliste accomply,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[22]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[22]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[22]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui de tout sera bien remply,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[23]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[5]/l[23]/text()[1]", "text": "Poura m’instruire à fonds faisant un tour d’allée."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[6]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Il s’arresta là un moment, comme pour reprendre haleine, puis il poursuivit aussi-tost sans me donner le temps de parler."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "D’autres croyant dire merveilles"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[2]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Disent cent sottises pareilles."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Tel ne manquant jamais, dit l’un, de tout sçavoir,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[4]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "De la Compagnie est l’espoir."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Enfin tous ces grands esprits fermes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour s’expliquer ont quantité de termes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Comme, aujourd’huy sur les Bureaux"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Nous n’avons rien mis de nouveau,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "La Compagnie a toutes ces Nouvelles,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur le Bureau l’on en mit hier de belles,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Ou sur le Bureau doit s’ouvrir à l’instant,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "On doit tantost en examiner telles,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Car le Bureau n’est encor que de tant,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Telle Nouvelle n’est pas mure,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Telle est aujourd’huy dans son plain,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Telle est aux abois, & demain"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Telle seulement sera seure."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "Tels ne sachant rien des premiers,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[19]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[19]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne sont que de francs regratiers,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[20]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[20]/text()[1]", "text": "Et les bonnes toûjours leur estant inconnuës,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[21]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[21]/text()[1]", "text": "Ils ne sçavent que les menuës,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[22]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[6]/l[22]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’ils debitent tous les derniers."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[7]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Hé bien qu’en dites-vous, me dit-il en me regardant fixement, apres avoir achevé ce Couplet ? Je suis surpris, luy repartis-je, de ce que vous avez trouvé tant de termes differens pour une chose que l’on ne croit pas qui en ait. J’ay bien examiné ces Messieurs, me répondit-il, & j’ay remarqué… Il s’interrompit à cet endroit ; & voyant un amas de Gens qui commençoient à former un peloton, il crut que l’on alloit debiter quelques Nouvelles, & il y courut avec plus d’empressement que n’en avoient tous ceux qu’il dépeignoit dans sa Comedie."}]}]}